OL,6,FThe deputy police and crime
OL,7,Fcommissioner for Devon, Cornwall and
OL,8,Fthe Isles of Scilly has resigned, five
OL,9,Fmonths after his appointment.
OL,11,FFormer Torbay Conservative councillor
OL,12,FMark Kingscote was hired by police and
OL,13,Fcrime commissioner (PCC) Alison
OL,14,FHernandez in July to assist her while
OL,15,Fshe dealt with leadership issues in
OL,16,Fthe force.
OL,18,FThe police and crime panel, which
OL,19,Fscrutinises her work, did not back Mr
OL,20,FKingscote's appointment at July's
OL,21,Fconfirmation hearing.
