OL,6,FThey said he didn't "have sufficient
OL,7,Fexperience that he would be unable to
OL,8,Fwork on behalf of all residents of
OL,9,FDevon, Cornwall and the Isles of
OL,10,FScilly...(or) meet the minimum
OL,11,Frequirements of the post".
OL,13,FThey recommended he shouldn't get the
OL,14,F#59,000-a-year job, but Ms Hernandez
OL,15,Fappointed him anyway. Just months
OL,16,Flater, he has gone.
OL,18,FMs Hernandez said in a letter to panel
OL,19,Fmembers that Mr Kingscote had resigned
OL,20,F"due to personal circumstances".
