OL,6,FShe did not disclose what those
OL,7,Fcircumstances are - but in a letter to
OL,8,Fpolice and crime panel members, Ms
OL,9,FHernandez wrote: "I am particularly
OL,10,Fgrateful for his assistance on
OL,11,Fscrutinising our estates' plans,
OL,12,Fattending public and civic engagement
OL,13,Fevents, the police museum and many
OL,14,Fother matters."
OL,16,FShe is not expecting to recruit
OL,17,Fanother deputy in the near future.
