OL,6,FWhen selecting Mr Kingscote, in the
OL,7,Fface of the strong recommendation of
OL,8,Fthe police and crime panel against the
OL,9,Fappointment, Ms Hernandez claimed her
OL,10,Fdeputy had "a unique set of skills"
OL,11,Fincluding working with people with
OL,12,Fcomplex mental health needs over his
OL,13,F30-year career in the NHS.
OL,15,FShe said he would focus on issues such
OL,16,Fas anti-social behaviour issues in
OL,17,FTorbay, while she concentrated on the
OL,18,Fleadership of an organisation "in dire
OL,19,Fstraits".
