OL,3,CDeputy police and crime commissioner
OL,4,Cresigns after five months in role
OL,6,FAt the time of Mr Kingscote's
OL,7,Fappointment, chief constable Will Kerr
OL,8,Fhad been suspended over allegations of
OL,9,Fserious sexual assault in Northern
OL,10,FIreland, which he strenuously denies.
OL,12,FDeputy chief constable Jim Colwell
OL,13,Fstepped up automatically to act as
OL,14,Fchief constable, but then was himself
OL,15,Fsuspended in November last year over
OL,16,Fclaims he misused his work phone.
