OL,3,CDeputy police and crime commissioner
OL,4,Cresigns after five months in role
OL,6,FBoth the permanent chief constable and
OL,7,Fthe acting chief constable are now
OL,8,Fsubjects of separate investigations by
OL,9,Fthe Independent Office of Police
OL,10,FConduct.
OL,12,FLast month, Ms Hernandez appointed
OL,13,Fformer chief of Dorset police James
OL,14,FVaughan as interim chief constable,
OL,15,Fsaying the move would be welcomed by
OL,16,Fresidents, police officers and staff.
