OL,6,FMs Hernandez has the power to appoint
OL,7,Fa deputy without the panel's support
OL,8,Fbut apologised to the panel after
OL,9,Finforming journalists of the
OL,10,Fappointment before notifying them.
OL,12,FThe police and crime commissioner's
OL,13,Foffice says it will not comment about
OL,14,FMr Kingscote's resignation as it is "a
OL,15,Fstaff matter".
OL,17,FChair of the police and crime panel
OL,18,FCllr Sally Haydon (Lab, Plymouth City
OL,19,FCouncil) said she is" surprised and
OL,20,Fdisappointed, given all the motions we
OL,21,Fwent through at the time".
