OL,4,Cresigns after five months in role
OL,6,FShe maintained the view she expressed
OL,7,Flast July that she would rather the
OL,8,Fdeputy PCC's salary be spent on "more
OL,9,Fbobbies on the beat".
OL,11,FThe role was expected to run for 12
OL,12,Fmonths, with the option of extending
OL,13,Fit until 2028, when elections are next
OL,14,Fheld for the police and crime
OL,15,Fcommissioner, which is a political
OL,16,Fappointment. Ms Hernandez, a
OL,17,FConservative, was elected last year
OL,18,Ffor the third time.
